Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:37.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:95700,97285}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:39.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:97827,99787}Good morning, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:42.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100079,102790}That was some design contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:44.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102790,104250}You took first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:46.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:104959,106753}It was a good design.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:48.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106753,108338}I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:54.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108338,114302}It was such a gorgeous dress,\NI wish I could wear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:58.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114510,118139}I'm sure Miki will let\Nyou if you ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:00.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:118348,120642}You think so?\NThen I'll go ask. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:04.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123144,124062}I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:06.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:124896,126856}I told you I haven't heard anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126856,128274}Asuka, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:11.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129400,131069}We have a bet, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131069,132111}A bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:22.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138076,142288}Your part: when you get a challenge\Nfrom St. Tail, let me know right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142288,144248}Don't try to cheat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145541,147835}I'm not going to cheat!\NGeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:30.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149379,150588}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:34.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154008,154717}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:45.26,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:162892,165269}You Confessed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:50.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169273,170274}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:53.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170650,173236}Good morning. You're looking well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:57.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173236,177240}Um, I'm sorry,\NI couldn't help overhearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:00.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177699,180702}Do you and Junior\Nhave a bet going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:03.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180702,183705}Is it for ice cream?\NOr maybe a hamburger?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:06.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185123,186708}You really want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:12.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188876,192171}At the contest the other day…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:18.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192714,198845}{\i1}If Meimi isn't St. Tail,\Nthen I'll stop following her.{NOTE:retrospective}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:22.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200888,202181}{\i1}You promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:26.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202557,206686}{\i1}But if I'm right, you have to date me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:27.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206686,207395}{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:29.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208771,209647}{\i1}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:31.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209897,211399}{\i1}What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:40.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213943,220074}Which means, if I prove you\Nare St. Tail, then I win the bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:46.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223244,226539}I don't give up easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:56.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230501,236007}In y=-2x+4 reversed,\Ny equals one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:04:04.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236924,244932}Furthermore, in 2x+y=4, x equals…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:07.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246642,247894}{\i1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248352,250855}{\i1}Why'd you make such a bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252231,254317}Miss Haneoka? Miss Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255943,257403}Miss Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257403,258780}Were you paying attention?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:22.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259697,262283}Come here and solve this problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:23.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262658,263826}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:27.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265328,267246}That's because\Nyou're always daydreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:30.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269582,270500}Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271542,273461}What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283054,284639}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:49.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284639,289352}And I thought we did such a good job of\Nfooling Miss Takamiya at the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:52.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290186,292188}I just don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292939,294524}Why'd he make the bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:55.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294524,295608}I…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299695,302031}I certainly don't\Nwant to be caught now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:05.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302865,305034}You mean you wanted to\Nat one time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:06.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305034,306410}Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:08.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307495,308913}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:12.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308913,312750}Recently, a man came\Nto me seeking help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:15.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312750,315294}I didn't know if I should tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:19.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316963,319674}His name is Mr. Kanamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:26.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321843,326180}His grandfather had\Nrecently passed away,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:31.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326180,331060}leaving him a jewel in his will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331811,333062}And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:40.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333646,340069}Then some relatives rewrote the will\Nand took the jewel from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:42.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340570,342196}How cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:50.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344907,350705}They have lied to him,\Nsaying they will put it in safekeeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:53.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350705,353833}But in actuality,\Nthey have put it up for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:06:02.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355585,362341}Mr. Kanamori went to see those relatives\Nto get his jewel back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:06.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363593,366137}{\i1}Uncle, Auntie! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:08.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366137,368598}{\i1}Please, give it back! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:21.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374103,381736}He desperately wants to get\Nthe jewel before it is sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:26.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382862,386532}I wish I could help,\Nbut Miss Takamiya is…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:31.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386532,391704}The way things are going,\Nshe and Asuka will never settle the bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:35.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392413,395875}Because St. Tail\Nwon't be caught easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:39.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396751,399503}But then Miss Takamiya\Nwill keep following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:43.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400504,403090}What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403090,404759}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406052,407970}Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:51.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409347,411807}I have an excellent idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:10.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429116,430326}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431869,433120}I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:14.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433120,434038}Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:20.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439627,440878}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:23.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442380,443798}Hey, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444548,445383}Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446258,447802}What is it, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:31.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447802,451806}You said you like my hands because they\Nlook like a magician's hands, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:32.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451806,452473}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:35.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452473,455101}Then… take my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:37.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456143,457520}Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:38.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457520,458354}Yes. And then…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458354,459939}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:42.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459939,462692}You want me to close my eyes,\Nyou've thought up a new trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:45.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462692,465653}I'll count to three,\Nthen you can open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:46.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465653,466529}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467113,468155}You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:48.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468155,468531}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:50.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469490,470032}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:51.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470783,471534}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475663,477748}Mama! How'd you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:02.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480710,482336}This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:06.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482336,486215}Isn't it? I'm sure\Nthis trick will be a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:10.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486882,490678}This sort of trick\Nhas been done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:15.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491137,495057}But never while holding hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495057,496475}This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:18.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496475,498978}Absolutely fantastic!\NShow me how to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:19.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498978,499812}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:20.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499812,500896}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:25.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501480,505109}Because it is the fruit of our labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:29.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505526,509113}You could say it is\Na symbol of our love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515745,517288}Hey, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517288,518039}Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:42.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519123,522501}I thought you were leaving early!\NYou're gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:47.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523335,527590}Jeez. And he just has\Nto have ham and eggs on Wednesdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:04.35,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:541854,544356}I will visit Kanamori's house tonight\Nto steal the jewel. – St. Tail
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:14.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551906,554700}Why's the note burnt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554700,556702}Cause it was in my breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:17.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556702,557912}Oh, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557912,560081}I have a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:25.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560790,565377}We lure St. Tail into our trap by\Nplaying on her weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:27.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565377,567421}You'll help, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:29.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567421,569048}I don't know what your plan is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:32.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569882,572051}But I want no part of it if it's sneaky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:36.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573052,576597}Oh, all right.\NIf you won't help, I'll do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:577348,578265}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:47.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583437,587108}You do want to settle\Nour bet, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:49.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587108,589735}Then don't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:54.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592822,594532}Give me your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:58.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594532,598577}This will just be between\NSt. Tail and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:01.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600496,601622}Have it your way!
Comment: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:04.62,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:604625,604625}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:10.63,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:610631,610631}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:15.63,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:615636,615636}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:26.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622101,626021}Lord forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630901,632027}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:35.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634363,635698}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:39.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637658,639577}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:55.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653841,655426}Meimi, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:58.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657136,658262}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:01.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658846,661432}Did you concoct another of\Nyour strange colognes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:05.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662183,665895}It will come in handy tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:13.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670107,673861}May the blessings of God be with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:18.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675779,678199}No! Never! Absolutely no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:22.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678991,682161}Why do I have to go outside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:26.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682494,686123}You promised, remember?\NYou said you wouldn't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:31.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688250,691086}You're not going back\Non your word, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:36.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692713,696133}Now Asuka, you wait\Noutside the room. Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702431,703933}Is everything under control?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:44.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703933,704767}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:48.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705684,708938}Shouldn't we guard the inside, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:51.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708938,711815}No, just the outside.\NThose are Miss Takamiya's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:57.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714109,717571}Darn that Takamiya!\NShe got her nerve, ordering me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:12.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729375,732628}Okay, he's here alone.\NHe's my target.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:16.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735547,736799}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:26.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744014,746058}Sorry, but I need your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:33.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751689,753232}{\i1}It's so dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754900,757069}{\i1}That must be the heirloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:42.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759321,762700}{\i1}Strange. Asuka Jr. isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:52.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770541,772167}{\i1}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778090,780342}{\i1}What happened?!\NWho did this to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:08.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786598,788600}Fooled you, didn't I?\NSaint Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:11.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789184,791103}{\i1}T-Takamiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:14.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791437,794064}Now, let's see your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:20.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795858,800029}Asuka! I know you're here!\NWe're finally going to see her face!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806493,808746}The switch… is over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808746,810622}Hurry, turn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817421,818714}St. Tail is…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:40.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820341,820924}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:42.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821633,822176}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:46.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823052,826013}Oh no!\NYou're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:47.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826347,827848}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:53.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831310,833354}Asuka, hurry, turn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:56.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833687,836106}I'm arresting her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:57.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836106,837691}Don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:11.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850037,851330}Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:14.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851455,854041}This is St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:19.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857127,859505}What went wrong?\NI was right, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:21.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861048,861924}A mustache?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:40.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878190,880692}A man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:47.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884446,887157}St. Tail's… a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:53.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890119,893122}It wasn't Meimi. It's a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893497,894123}One…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:55.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894581,895124}Two…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:56.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895332,896291}Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:901088,903215}I wonder if I overdid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:07.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:903757,907010}Sorry, I'm taking this jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:29.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926071,929074}I thought I heard St. Tail's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932202,934538}Nah, probably just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:51.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946216,951013}{\i1}The cat-burglar… I've been\Nafter all this time… is a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:53.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951013,953515}{\i1}And a transvestite at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:10.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968614,970866}It can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:21.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977915,981376}{\i1}"I must speak to you, but you\Nmust promise not to come close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:24.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981376,984796}{\i1}Please come to D Park.\N– St. Tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:27.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986840,987633}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:38.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995224,998977}{\i1}I really don't want to see that man.\NBut I guess I'll go see what he has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:13.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030384,1033387}Good evening!\NI'll bet you had quite a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:19.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036515,1039226}You guys were trying to trap me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:21.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040227,1041687}That's why you were punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:25.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043689,1045107}Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:26.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045691,1046984}A girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:33.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050279,1053740}If you've had enough, don't try to\Ndiscover my identity any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:38.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056326,1058161}Just forget all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:42.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059705,1062749}I know it seemed like\NI was in cahoots with Takamiya,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:44.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062749,1064001}but there was nothing I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:46.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064918,1066128}We had a bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:47.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066628,1067588}A bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:50.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068255,1070048}Takamiya made this bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:52.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070716,1072926}If I won,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:56.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072926,1076263}she promised to stop\Nfollowing Haneoka around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:03.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080934,1083020}Haneoka's one of my classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:05.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083020,1085439}Sure, she's kind of noisy…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:07.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085439,1087983}But I don't think following her\Naround all the time is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:13.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092446,1093947}That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:18.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095449,1098910}That's not why I'm angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:24.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099870,1104124}That's not why I'm angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:28.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106460,1108670}I'm gonna arrest her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:31.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110464,1111923}That's not…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:35.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113133,1115385}Oh, did you want to be caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:37.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116678,1117929}What I meant…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:43.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121224,1123602}I didn't want to be caught by her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:45.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124186,1125979}If… If I…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:51.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127439,1131568}If I'm going to be caught by anyone,\NI want to be caught by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135906,1137032}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137032,1138200}Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:05.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143163,1145499}{\i1}What did she mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:10.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149461,1150671}Anyway…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:14.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152547,1154508}What a relief! St. Tail's a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:18.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155676,1158720}I'm not telling Takamiya about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:54.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192337,1194631}St. Tail was a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:58.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195215,1198176}Which means,\NI win the bet, Takamiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:19:59.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198176,1199469}Yes. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199469,1201638}You'd better keep your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:04.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202806,1204224}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:05.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204224,1205600}See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:07.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206184,1207436}Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:09.22,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1206852,1209229}{\fad(500,500)}Guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211857,1213525}What kind of bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:26.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223744,1226496}{\i1}If I'm going to be caught by anyone,\NI want to be caught by you!{NOTE:retrospective}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:34.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231710,1234463}{\i1}What's gotten into me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:36.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234463,1236757}{\i1}She's nowhere near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:42.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240385,1242345}None of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:45.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243513,1245599}You're always so rude!
